g= h(S) = G + f(S)u
E(g) = E\left[G + f(S)u\right] = G+ E\left(E\left [f(S)u|S\right]\right) = G+ E\left(f(S)E\left [u|S\right]\right) = G + 0 = G 
gg' = \left[G + f(S)u\right]\left[G + f(S)u\right]' = GG' + Gu'f(S)'+f(S)uG'+ f(S)uu'f(S)'
\Rightarrow E(gg') = GG' + E\Big (EGu'f(S)'|S\Big)+ E\Big (Ef(S)uG'|S\Big)+ E\Big(Ef(S)uu'f(S)'|S\Big)
=GG' + E\Big (GE(u'|S)f(S)'\Big)+ E\Big (f(S)E(u|S)G'\Big)+ E\Big(f(S)E(uu'|S)f(S)'\Big)
=GG' + 0 + 0 + E\Big(f(S)E(uu'|S)f(S)'\Big)
